REDUX INSTRUCTIONS

-- install redux - npm instull redux react-redux
1. Create a store - where all your data would be stored
2. Create a reducer and pass it as an arguement to the store
3. Provide your store to the App.js component
4. Use/access the store date from any component
5. Dispatch action from the respective component



REDUX TOOLKIT INSTRUCTIONS
--install redux toolkit - npm install @reduxjs/toolkit
1. combine reducer and action into a slice
2. replace createStore() with configureStore()
3. Update useSelected() and useDispatch() on the component.